"arabic", "text_bw": "gamorN", "text_ar": "غَمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[when thus used; or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a submerging deep, a deep place,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an abyss,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of water]: (TA:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gimaArN", "text_ar": "غِمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumuwrN", "text_ar": "غُمُورٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S, K.) You say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "baHorN gamorN", "text_ar": "بَحْرٌ غَمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "An abundant sea:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and [in the pl.]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "biHaArN gimaArN", "text_ar": "بِحَارٌ غِمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumuwrN", "text_ar": "غُمُورٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) And of a thing that has become much, you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*aA kaviyrN", "text_ar": "هٰذَا كَثِيرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamiyrN", "text_ar": "غَمِيرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This is much."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Algamari", "text_ar": "الغَمَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] ―         -b2-  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "main of the sea:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) pl. as above. (TA.)       -A2-  (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Liberal in disposition:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, * TA:) pl. as above: (TA:) and in like manner,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamoru Alxuluqi", "text_ar": "غَمْرُ الخُلُقِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) or this last, and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamoru Albadiyhapi", "text_ar": "غَمْرُ البَدِيهَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", signify (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "abounding in beneficence:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "pl. as above: (S, K: [see also"}, 