nd": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamaArN", "text_ar": "غَمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "are afterwards there added: but most probably these only (without"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "p", "text_ar": "ة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ") are correct:]) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamorapN", "text_ar": "غَمْرَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumaArN", "text_ar": "غُمَارٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamaArN", "text_ar": "غَمَارٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signify"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a crowding,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pressing,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "of men, (S, Msb,) and of water: (S:) the pl. of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamorapN", "text_ar": "غَمْرَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gimaArN", "text_ar": "غِمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) You say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~aAsi", "text_ar": "النَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "daxalotu fiY gumaAri", "text_ar": "دَخَلْتُ فِى غُمَارِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamaArihimo", "text_ar": "غَمَارِهِمْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb, TA,) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamarihimo", "text_ar": "غَمَرِهِمْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I entered among the crowding,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "pressing, of the people,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and their multitude:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, TA;) as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fY xamarihimo", "text_ar": "فى خَمَرِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "xumaArihimo", "text_ar": "خُمَارِهِمْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.] (TA.) And ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^akuwnu fiY gumaAri", "text_ar": "اَكُونُ فِى غُمَارِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~aAsi", "text_ar": "النَّاسِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I shall be among the dense congregation of the people,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "occurs in a trad. (TA.)       -A4-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".       -A5-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "layolN gamorN", "text_ar": "لَيْلٌ غَمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Intensely dark night."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["K", "ISd", "TA", "IAth", "S", "Msb"]}, {"entry_id": "n32390", "headword_ar": "غُمْرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumurN", "text_ar": "غُمُرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, ISd) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamorN", "text_ar": "غَمْرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gimorN", "text_ar": "غِمْرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", accord. to the K, but this last is unknown, (TA,) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamarN", "text_ar": "غَمَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamirN", "text_ar": "غَمِرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) originally, A boy"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "devoid of intelligence:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and hence, (Msb,) a man (S, Msb)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "inexperienced in affairs:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "ignorant:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "inexperienced in war and in counsel; not rendered firm,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sound, in judgment, by experience:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L:) one"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in whom is no profit nor judgment:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(ISd, TA:) one"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in whom is no good nor profit with respect to intelligence or judgment or work:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AZ, Msb:) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mugam~arN", "text_ar": "مُغَمَّرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies the same as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, TA;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "deemed ignorant:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) the fem. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is with"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "p", "text_ar": "ة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, Msb;) and so is that of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamirN", "text_ar": "غَمِرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (TA:) and the pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^agomaArN", "text_ar": "اَغْمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, Msb, TA;) and this may also be pl. of ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamarN", "text_ar": "غَمَرٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", like as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^asobaAbN", "text_ar": "اَسْبَابٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is pl. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sababN", "text_ar": "سَبَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.)       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorapN", "text_ar": "غُمْرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["S", "Msb", "K", "ISd", "TA", "L", "AZ"]}, {"entry_id": "n32391", "headword_ar": "غِمْرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Concealed enmity and violent hatred,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rancour, malevolence, malice,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "spite."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamira", "text_ar": "غَمِرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Thirst:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb:) pl."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^agomaArN", "text_ar": "اَغْمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (S.) El-'Ajjáj says,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "Hat~aY A_i*aA maAbal~ati AlA^agomaAraA"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Until, when they damped"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "their"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thirst"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bal~ati AlA_ibilu A^agomaArahaA", "text_ar": "بَلَّتِ الاـِبِلُ اَغْمَارَهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The camels drank a little."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["S", "Msb"]}, {"entry_id": "n32392", "headword_ar": "غَمَرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A drowning; being drowned:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "so in the phrase"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "mawotu Algamari", "text_ar": "مَوْتُ الغَمَرِ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Death by drowning."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.)       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamorN", "text_ar": "غَمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".       -A3-  The"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "foul smell of flesh-meat,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and its grease adhering to the hand:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) and the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smell of fish."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) Hence,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "minodiylu", "text_ar": "مِنْدِيلُ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Algamari", "text_ar": "الغَمَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Mgh)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The napkin,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "rough napkin, with which the hand is cleansed therefrom."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L, TA.)       -A4-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in two places."}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n32393", "headword_ar": "غَمِرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "[part. n. of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamira", "text_ar": "غَمِرَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. You say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yadN gamirapN", "text_ar": "يَدٌ غَمِرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A hand foul with the smell of flesh-meat,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and with the grease thereof adhering to it."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "sahikN", "text_ar": "سَهِكٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]       -A2-  See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in two places.       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gamirapN", "text_ar": "غَمِرَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as an epithet applied to a she-camel, see voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gabirN", "text_ar": "غَبِرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": ["S", "K"]}, {"entry_id": "n32394", "headword_ar": "غُمَرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A small drinking-cup"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bowl,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with which people divided the water among themselves in a journey when they had little of it;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and this they [sometimes] did by putting a pebble into a vessel, and then pouring into it as much water as would cover the pebble, and giving it to each man among them: (TA:) or the"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "smallest of drinking-cups"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bowls:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K:) [see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qaEobN", "text_ar": "قَعْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tibonN", "text_ar": "تِبْنٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":] accord. to ISh,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it contains twice"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thrice the quantity of the measure called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kiylajap", "text_ar": "كِيلَجَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": [but this seems to be a large"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gmr", "text_ar": "غمر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", used for watering a horse; and the words which here immediately follow are app. not added by ISh, but relate to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gmr", "text_ar": "غمر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "used by a man for himself or for another man:] the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qaEob", "text_ar": "قَعْب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is larger than it, and satisfies the thirst of a man: the pl. is"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^agomaArN", "text_ar": "اَغْمَارٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (TA.) El-Aashà of Báhileh says, in an elegy on his brother ElMunteshir Ibn-Wahb,"}, {"kind": "quote", "text": "takofiyhi Huz~apu filo*K A_ino A^alom~a bihaA\n                      \n                     \n                        mina Al$~iwaA='i wayurowiY $urobahu Algumaru"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A slice of camel's liver, roasted, if he lighted upon it, used to suffice him; and the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumar", "text_ar": "غُمَر"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "used to satisfy his thirst"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S, TA.) And Mohammad is related, in a trad., to have said,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laA tajoEaluwniY kagumari Alr~aAkibi", "text_ar": "لَا تَجْعَلُونِى كَغُمَرِ الرَّاكِبِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Sal~uwA EalaY A^aw~ala Ald~uEaA='i waA^awosaTahu waA=xirahu", "text_ar": "صَلُّوا عَلَى اَوَّلَ الدُّعَا=ءِ وَاَوْسَطَهُ وَا=خِرَهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Make ye me not like the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumar", "text_ar": "غُمَر"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of the rider: salute me in the beginning of prayer and in the middle thereof and in the end thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "meaning that they should not make the salutation of him to be a thing of no great importance, and to be postponed: for the rider puts on his camel his saddle and his travel-ling-provisions, and last of all hangs upon his saddle his drinking-cup. (IAth, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "K", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n32395", "headword_ar": "غُمُرٌ", "root": "gmr", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "gumorN", "text_ar": "غُمْرٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": []}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}